d anthropology.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGifts, Spiritual. 0aJustification (Christian theology)xHistory of doctrinesy16th century. 4aKulturanthropologie. 4aLuther, Martin. 4aReziprozität. 4aSystematische Theologie. 7aRELIGION / Christian Theology / Systematic.2bisacsh  aCultural anthropology.  aLuther, Martin.  areciprocity.  asystematic theology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Theology and Religious Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110638165oZDB-23-GTR08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2006z9783110277128oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET THEOLOGIE/RELIGIONSWISS./JUDAISTIK  2006z9783110277043oZDB-23-DGF08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket Reformationz9783110551693oZDB-23-FJR0 cprintz978311018839440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311091933240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110919332423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110919332/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2006  aZDB-23-DGGb2006  aZDB-23-FJR  aZDB-23-GTRc2000d2014